OL,3,CDerbyshire man one of first to access
OL,4,Cnew 'life-changing' Parkinson's drug
OL,6,FA man from Derbyshire living with
OL,7,FParkinson's disease has said that the
OL,8,Feffects of a new drug have changed his
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FDamian Gath, who is 52, was offered
OL,12,Fthe treatment at Kings Mill Hospital
OL,13,Fin Nottinghamshire and he is one of
OL,14,Fonly six people in the UK to be
OL,15,Ftreated with the drug.
