OL,3,CDerbyshire man one of first to access
OL,4,Cnew 'life-changing' Parkinson's drug
OL,6,FHe was first diagnosed with
OL,7,FParkinson's in 2014 and originally
OL,8,Fthought what he felt was a sports
OL,9,Finjury. He said he could barely
OL,10,Fcomprehend what he was being told when
OL,11,Fdoctors first diagnosed him with
OL,12,FParkinson's disease.
OL,14,FUntil very recently when he first
OL,15,Fstarted having treatment, Damian's
OL,16,Fsymptoms were so severe that he was
OL,17,Ftaking fourteen tablets a day to try
OL,18,Fand suppress them. He described the
OL,19,Fpain he was in as "excruciating".
