OL,3,CDerbyshire man one of first to access
OL,4,Cnew 'life-changing' Parkinson's drug
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, Damian
OL,7,Fsaid the effects of his new medication
OL,8,Fhave been "life-changing".
OL,10,F"I've gone from not being able to do
OL,11,Fsimple day-to-day tasks to performing
OL,12,Fday-to-day tasks", he said.
OL,14,F"I mean there were times before where
OL,15,FI could do those tasks but I had to
OL,16,Fwait for the precise point in the day
OL,17,Fwhere I knew I was capable of doing
OL,18,Fit."
