OL,3,CDerbyshire man one of first to access
OL,4,Cnew 'life-changing' Parkinson's drug
OL,6,FDamian is the first person in the East
OL,7,FMidlands to receive the new drug,
OL,8,Fwhich is called produodopa.
OL,10,FIt drug helps manage the symptoms of
OL,11,FParkinson's disease and is an infusion
OL,12,Fthat enters the bloodstream of the
OL,13,Fpatient under the skin, controlled by
OL,14,Fa pump that releases the drug 24 hours
OL,15,Fa day. Damian says he felt the drug
OL,16,Fgave him near "instant results".
