OL,3,CDerbyshire man one of first to access
OL,4,Cnew 'life-changing' Parkinson's drug
OL,6,FSpeaking on how he felt after his new
OL,7,Ftreatment, Damian said: "I haven't
OL,8,Fstopped crying for three weeks, Its
OL,9,Fbeen so emotional. My family and
OL,10,Ffriends have been so supportive
OL,11,Fthey're so happy for me. My children
OL,12,Fare just blown away from it".
OL,14,F"I've gone from 10% to 90% in the last
OL,15,Fthree weeks", he explained. "I could
OL,16,Feven consider getting back to work
OL,17,Fthat's the big thing. And cooking a
OL,18,Fmeal for family and friends, a good
OL,19,Fmeal not beans on toast or a microwave
OL,20,Fmeal, a proper meal".
