OL,3,CDerbyshire man one of first to access
OL,4,Cnew 'life-changing' Parkinson's drug
OL,6,FDamian said that being one of the
OL,7,Ffirst to try the drug was an honour.
OL,9,FRowan Wathes, the Director of Policy
OL,10,Fand Health Strategy at Parkinson's UK,
OL,11,Fsaid she expects nearly 900 people to
OL,12,Fbenefit and for those people they
OL,13,Fshould, looking at Damian, "be
OL,14,Foptimistic".
OL,16,FAlthough Damian is currently only one
OL,17,Fof a handful in the country with
OL,18,Faccess to the new drug, it's hoped it
OL,19,Fwill be rolled out across the country
OL,20,Fso more people can benefit.
